AWP STATION BY UNREAL A basic AWP map, simetrical, fun and exciting. Made for competitive purposes, includes a few features like moving trains on the middle, that will appear randomly and will make everyround diferent from the previous one. Based on VALVEs de_train map. Map features: - cubemaps - HDR - interactive environment (moving train) - ambient sounds - lighning - detail
Thanks to Hybrid and Matuka for supporting me, and providing constructive feedback on the map.
